    <step order="3" name="Author DTO Enum Change">
      Add `AvailableInContexts` C# enum: `[Flags]` or plain — choose to align with `ToolContext ∋ X` set semantics (FR-07 "set-based" `∋` notation suggests flags). Add field to `AnalysisTool` record (nullable for migration safety; serialize as option-set value).
    </step>
    <step order="4" name="Author Dataverse Column Change">
      Add option-set column `sprk_availableincontexts` to `sprk_analysistool`. Values: 1=Playbook (default), 2=Chat, 4=Both (flag semantics) OR enum semantics — match the C# choice. Document in task notes.
    </step>
